Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:34.46,Default,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H00FFFF&\pos(533,351)}{\fs26}Together Forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:35.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:38.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I think about Otani's exam tomorrow, the more worried I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I should send him a message of encouragement...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.23,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, this is for real. You got mail.{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:48.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:54.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I called around, but no one else could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:55.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure. Just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that's your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Otani-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:10.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:12.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I just have one question...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:13.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's not about height.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with someone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your insults elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:19.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? We have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just explaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, oh dear, oh dear. My, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:28.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's no need to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:31.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. He was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:32.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, n-n-nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:40.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, uh... Koizumi's... I mean... R-R-Risa's boyfriend, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I haven't prepared anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go to any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:45.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:49.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm only just over 156cm.\N I'm sorry. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:50.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with someone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't refer to me as "this."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:57.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... sorry to impose on you like this, asking to stay over so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:02:59.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, let me explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any ulterior motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, he has an exam tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:08.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but everyone in his family has come down with influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So it isn't what you think. Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:12.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My, that is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, but where will he sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he could sleep in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean, I'll sleep in a different room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think! I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I seem totally suspicious, don't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing, ending up like this the day before the exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing stuff like this... like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.97,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. Calm down.{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll greet them properly next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:50.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate, I'll look like some useless guy who'd blow his exams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,just so he could fool around with his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I explained everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's not good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious about the strangest things, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand for halfheartedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But that aside, you should worry about your exam for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll want to study all night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go hang out in my brother's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm with you, I'll just end up talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:24.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an emergency, just call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:24.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,'kay. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Otani, he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he was chased out of his home the day before his exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,even if he had to meet my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Would you like something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I wake him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he sleeps for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyelashes are pretty long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani! Wake up, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is your exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,9:20am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already past 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How long does it take to get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take the train, it takes about an hour. If I rush now, I can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stuff! Your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wake me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:19.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,On TV they just said that the trains and buses aren't running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should you do, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:36.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My life has been a mess since I was chased out of my house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:45.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much of it too... That's how unlucky I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:59.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the other examinees are snowed out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it's just you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:05.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you rambling on about? Get up! Stand up, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:08.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got the time for this,\N then why not run there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Takato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:13.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:13.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:14.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But the trains aren't running...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take the subway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:26.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is too mu-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jinx me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:36.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've worked so hard, Otani. I don't want to see it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether you pass or fail, as long as you do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste all of your effort up until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:46.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't ride tandem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! The subway!
