Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:10.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:11.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too loud, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, so you'll definitely be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Please, begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My future, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Been here long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The results will be out in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, Otani is free from the stress of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been on a date in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:52.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything is fine. Today I'm making it all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Making what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do anything while I was studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so today you can call the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:00.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:04.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:11.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:13.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got the old bag with you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:14.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, dressed up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Working?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shoot for a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a supermodel, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing an outdoor shoot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen a photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay? You'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:42.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to start shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You over there, you're being disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You're amazing, Mimi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:09.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:11.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A pro... You really are a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:17.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! I already told you I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these friends of yours, Mimi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The old lady is a total stranger. This is my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:29.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, let's use her in place of the amateur model.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:30.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:35.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who was going to participate couldn't make it. Let's have her fill in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Model?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:45.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. She's got the height, and she has nice style, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way, no way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:48.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, let's go with a girly look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for a really cute look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute? I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:06.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:13.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason... that person seems really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:23.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:26.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wonderful. Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. You look very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I really look cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:44.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Get out of my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:45.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you over there... Could you smile more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:01.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:02.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:06.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not suited to being a model at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not suited, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I do like watching stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work. You were really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:27.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea. That's all thanks to the skills of the stylist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the clothes you pick for me, Nakahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stylist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're flattering me, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels great working with you, Nakahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:53.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I found a job I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want to become a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:56.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You were way too stiff in front of the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think you were cute, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, well... just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a stylist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A stylist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a stretch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I do like helping people coordinate clothes and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Don't worry about whether you're suited to it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:23.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just decide that you like it and want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then draw on your confidence and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Otani-sensei guarantees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:38.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-sensei sure is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,there's the question of whether he can actually become a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka! Maity-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We went for a drive and decided to drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:51.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:57.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Risa's lover, and this is her man on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to innocent little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I've just been lied to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been in touch with Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The exam results come out today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I saw the midget earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,On the bench in front of the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I called out, "Hey midget!", but he didn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The short boy from the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Risa's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You're so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, have you talked to Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.84,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lied to again, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:44.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:48.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely failed. He is an idiot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing at other's misfortunes will bring you bad karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:53.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd pass first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed cannot be reached at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:09.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave a message after the tone, then press the pound sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? How many times do I have to tell you not to scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I need to leave early!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:23.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:25.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:31.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsubara-san, I'll cover for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohori-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry! You can dock my pay if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was that age once too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be lied to anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you failed, there's always next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:16:00.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right here with you, even if you need to study all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani... Geez, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Otani! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:45.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to die, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:48.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the test again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:48.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You can re-take the test next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:53.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed. Why do I have to take it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! I'm telling you that the university accepted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Why"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were looking depressed on the bench in front of the train station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was so relieved I feel asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The battery had run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:16.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I just woke up, and I was going to go over to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:22.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So you were accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:25.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "What's up with you" me, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling asleep, running out of battery...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:32.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how worried I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?! You're not supposed to make calls while you're at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:41.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually managed to pass, yet you say "No way! Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you got anything else to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:47.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:52.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, there's no need to cry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:08.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you, I wouldn't have tried so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:11.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's thanks to you that I passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:18.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you really are a worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani... congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:37.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has decided on their future paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, we'll all go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at the very end, I'm still running late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late for your own graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:03.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:13.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to rewrite your diplomas as "All Hanshin and Kyojin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that you're late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:26.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:30.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The valedictorian has come down with anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:39.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, it's my pleasure to introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:39.43,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two idiots still aren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:44.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,our valedictorian speech, to be delivered by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.48,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony will be over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:51.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be delivered by Otani Atsushi and Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is long. We have to read the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. The mic is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:05.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do half and half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you read the first half. I don't wanna start...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.05,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:12.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:16.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Quiet, quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:28.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,These past three years, our teachers have really taken care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to them that we've all grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to grow any taller, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, some of us have remained small.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:37.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:44.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, here at Maido Academy, we've made a lot of good memories
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:47.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and had many wonderful experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:52.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, we say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us are going far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:59.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us are going to part ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:16.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:22.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Let's have three cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have the comedy act cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hip-hip...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!{alpha timing here}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray!{alpha timing  here}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:47.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to meet you, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:51.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:54.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're with me, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:22:00.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:23.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
